revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->
{{High-use|29532}}

== Usage ==
An enhancement of {{tl|oldid}} which does not need the page title to be specified (since there are no oldid conflicts between pages) and which also allows linking to a specific section in the page.

Typical usage:
* {{tlx|oldid2|<var>Revision number</var>|<var>Label</var>}}

* {{tlx|oldid2|<var>Revision number</var>|<var>Section name</var>|<var>Label</var>}}

{| class="wikitable"
! Code
! Output
|-
| {{tlx|oldid2|123456789|External links|Pgp688's version of "Boston Latin School"}}
| {{oldid2|123456789|External links|Pgp688's version of "Boston Latin School"}}
|-
| {{tlx|oldid2|123456789}}
| {{oldid2|123456789}}
|-
| {{tlx|oldid2|123456789|Pgp688's version of "Boston Latin School"}}
| {{oldid2|123456789|Pgp688's version of "Boston Latin School"}}
|-
| {{tlx|oldid2|123456789|External links|<nowiki/>}}
| {{oldid2|123456789|External links|}}
|}

Note that if the third parameter is used, even if empty, the 2nd specifies the section of the page, instead, and the 3rd specifies the link text.

== Redirects ==
* {{tl|Revision link}}
* {{tl|Revlink}}

== See also ==
* {{tl|Oldid}}
* [[Special:Permalink]]
* {{tl|Cross-wiki oldid}}
* {{tl|Cross-wiki language oldid}}
* {{tl|Diff2}}
* [[Help:Permanent link]]

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- CATEGORIES HERE, THANKS -->

[[Category:Oldid templates]]
[[Category:Internal link templates]]

}}</includeonly>

